见。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"22dcf969db","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东八月八日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"eb82fd424e","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"814a652012","type":"paragraph","text":"有点修改，在第3页，第4页(七年改为八年)，第8页。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"e9cd7d5408","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛十七日","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"ca7798b51b","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"d855a11140","type":"paragraph","text":"即刻送刘、周、朱、林、彭真、乔木阅，即刻看一下，如同意我的那一些修改，即刻付印，务于今天下午至迟晚上发到各同志手里，以便他们明日带回去。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"27629a1993","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东八月十七日上午四时","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"}],"page":{"id":"51d0901ac9","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3","start":0,"end":0}},"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"04ef30154d","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东八月八日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"1ba5a1b6f8","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东八月十七日上午四时","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"2bb8be1a56","type":"paragraph","text":"八月八日，以一天时间改成反右倾机会主义那个决议，主要把我写的第三节，同第四节不调和的地方，改得协调起来，八日晚上交我看。以上两个决议，九号就要印发给一切同志付讨论了。你们则以九日十日两天时间转到写第三个文件，即写关于彭张错误的决议，十日下午交给我看(初稿)。时间紧了，要加紧工作。以上即照办，为盼！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"3b35129563","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"3b7b1f2253","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对八届八中全会关于开展增产节约运动的决议稿的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9b43a2e3c3"},{"id":"42e64087b9","type":"subtitle","text":"乔木同志：","index":7,"publicationId":"C